# core/

- Put money math, sync selection, export shaping, validation, and search/filter in `core/`, with a JUnit test.
- Use system `gradle test` in `core/`, not `./gradlew`.
- Edit `core/src/` only — never `core/bin/` (generated copies from searches).
- No Android imports in this module.
